nodes.text: Brinn was a Human male who served as groundskeeper of House Teraan during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire. When the House Teral estate was overrun by Killiks, Brinn tried use the insecticide mines until he was attacked by these insectoids. A Republic spacer was tasked by Alek Teral to recover the insecticide mines from Brinn's corpse.
